title: side_02_002_01
---
<<declare $player_spoke_to_police_first = true>>

<<if $player_spoke_to_police_first>>
    Mic:Can we go back yet,Captain? #line:0a6a177 
    <<set $player_spoke_to_police_first = false>>
    Sif:For bugs sake...NO,we have to wait for orders. #line:0c36bc3 
    Rigel:What happened? #line:05f525d 
    Mic:A MOUSE!He looks so different from the books!Can I touch your tail?Please!!  #line:013dc0c 
    Sif:Stop it,mic! #line:0ca6ce6 
    Sif:(whispers)A mammal,what an unlucky day... #line:0501dd6 
    Sif:None of your business,mammal.Leave. #line:0eb9163 
    Rigel:It seems there was a murder,a Cyberpsychosis,of course... #line:0764ced 
    Sif:Ho...How do you know?We have already moved the body away! #line:0a4ead5 
    Rigel:I have seem lots of scenes like this,trust me. #line:02b4ad5 
    Mic:Can I touch your fluffy tail?Please!! #line:0f0ee46 
    Sif:Please,mic! #line:080aca5 
    Sif:You are right,this morning,we receieved a report that someone is murdered under plain sight.When I and my team reached here,the body was so awlful that I can barely recognize which spieces he was... #line:0e2bf3b 
    Sif:...It took some time for our specialist to know that the murder has Cyberpsychosis but you just took a glance... #line:09023bb 
    Sif:You can't be some normal mammal as far as I can tell,so if you can help,We would be grateful. #line:0f7cd1e 
    Sif:Try heading EAST of the RUST CITY,some of my team has already traced there. #line:05c212e 
    Rigel:It's so dangerous to let a Cyberpsychos on the run,I should move now. #line:0347f24 
    Mic:(Looking at Rigel without a blink) #line:0234889 
    <<accept_quest "Side_02_002">>

<<else>>
    Sif:Safty travel,little mammal. #line:0ecb6b9 
    Mic:Safe...traveling! #line:0c1780d 
<<endif>>
