title:Lion_Start
---
<<declare $player_spoke_to_Lion = false>>

<<if $player_spoke_to_Lion is false>>
    Lion:Good,you came. #line:00ce04a 
    Lion:Recently our intel team has captured an encrypted message that the bugs are doing large-scale experiment about military-grade cyberlimb. #line:0c7da74 
    Lion:We fear they are planning their next invasion. #line:0781f64 
    Lion:In this situation,sending a diplomat team is not a wise choice. #line:06cfcb1 
    Lion:So we are asking you to go on a private investigation. #line:09092dd 
    <<set $player_spoke_to_Lion = true>>
    <<jump Lion_Middle>>

<<else>>
    Lion:Good hunting,Rigel. #line:0334cc2 
<<endif>>
===

title:Lion_Middle
---
Lion:Any Qusetion? #line:08410a3 
        -> Where are they doing this experiment? #line:006f37f 
            Lion:According to our intel team,the main focus is in the RUST CITY,the heart of their industrial complex. #line:0871780 
            Lion:There should be a secret lab there,We need you to gather the information,and find a way to infiltrate. #line:0fdd81d 
            <<jump Lion_Middle>>
        -> What exactly are they working on? #line:07cd1a6 
            Lion:We can't tell so far,but it seems they are developing BIOLOGICAL WEAPON for their soilders. #line:036b7ee 
            Lion:...that are capable to destroy mammal's biological structure in a second.  #line:0cea460 
            <<jump Lion_Middle>>
        -> I'm ready. #line:08ffb2d 
            Lion:Good. #line:0b0e4c6 
Lion:We will provide you an ID card that will allow you to enter and exit RUST CITY at any time. #line:0eec082 
Lion:Also,some money will be transferred to your account,use it wisely before the operation. #line:0a51e70 
Lion:And... #line:0a5d8cb 
Lion:...Maybe this is a bad time to mention... #line:02b4a03 
Lion:Rigel,do you remember "CINDERTAIL"? #line:05a541b 
Rigel:How can I forget this name?I make bad dreams about him endlessly after the war. #line:02cee14 
Lion:Yes,"Cindertail"...the bug who killed MEISSA,the captain of ORION. #line:009d008 
Lion:He reappeared...after a long disappearence since the end of the war. #line:03d56b4 
Rigel:I won't fail this time,I will clear my magzine through his throat... #line:014a605 
Rigel:I traced him for entire 7 years and he finally appeared... #line:09bd707 
Lion:Clam down,young mouse. #line:02cdf0a 
Lion:I understand your feeling,I lost my brother on the battlefield half century ago. #line:0287ae5 
Lion:But the lust of revenge,will only consume you,don't let it cloud your mind. #line:009f8ed 
Lion:Tell me when you are ready,Dismiss. #line:085cad6 
 <<accept_quest "main_001">>
 <<accept_quest "main_00A">>
===

title:Lion_Last
---
Lion:How's the preparation? #line:0161e86 
        -> I need more time.  #line:060cb02 
            Lion:Take your time,little mouse. #line:0cda29e 
            <<jump Lion_Middle>>
        -> I'm ready for the mission. #line:034058d 
            Lion:Good. #line:026e742 
            Lion:We can't send you into the rust city officially,but we can send you near the city. #line:0433d8b 
            Rigel:And I have to find a way into the city,right? #line:023b6ef 
            Lion:That's correct.As always. #line:0fe2d88 
            Lion:This way. #line:037ee24 
            <<jump Lion_Middle>>


===

title:Zig_Zag
---
Zig:STAND RIGHT THERE,mammal. #line:09ab7f7 
Zig:Disarm all your Communication systems.RIGHT NOW. #line:0bda183 
Zig:If I can see a single device transferring data with outside,my companion will shoot you to a hornet. #line:0fc9c01 
Rigel:Okay,Okay!Relax,All comms down! #line:0dbcbbb 
Zig:Wise choice.You have been sniffing around the lab.Who are you,and what do you want? #line:0090c3a 
Rigel:Name's Sam,have been a chip trafficker for many years,you can check my ID. #line:0f9f500 
Rigel:And don't need to worry about me,I want to enter the lab same as your guys,we can collaborate. #line:0df4f88 
Zag:boss,How... #line:0fdc736 
Zig:Trafficker always know how to negotiate,eh?True,I am a humble merchant who "borrows" other's good ware too,same as you. #line:054a429 
Zig:Recently the lab is doing something big,very big.My boys told me thousands of valuable material are transported there everyday. #line:05cbb8c 
Zig:It's risky,but if we can manage to "borrow" a tiny portion of it...I can't even imagine!! #line:0109347 
Zig:But business is business,to prove your capability,we need you to do something for us,and we can discuss more after that. #line:09e6021 
Rigel:(Here we go again...) #line:0eb6480 
Zig:I need a special chip that can see through the wall of the lab,without it,it would be reckless to proceed. #line:0bcc7f5 
Zig:This can be circulated in the black market of your mammal country... #line:06665ba 
Zig:...or you can "borrow" it from the leaders of the local gang in the deep sewers,one of them must have it. #line:0858262 
Zig:I will send you my code,contact me once you finished. #line:076978f 
Zig:Good Luck. #line:0031041 
===

title:Zag_Comment
---
Zag:A word,boss? #line:08a83bf 
Zig:Zag,This is not the right time! #line:063795e 
Zag:It's about Sam,the way he fought,it's nothing I have seemed before. #line:0d125a9 
Zag:I have been in the army for a couple of years,and I saw lots of fights.This...This is something I have NEVER seem before. #line:063b3d3 
Zag:His movement,his way of using weapons and tactics...it's ART. #line:00ad1dd 
Zag:Like playing a chess game,he can always kill opponent's general with the shortest steps. #line:07a17b6 
Zag:I dare to say that if we have someone like him during the war,maybe tide of the war would have been on our side. #line:08128a9 
Zig:What the hell?!Zag,are you speaking for dirty mammals? #line:070f8fa 
Zig:But it does make sense.How can a trafficker fought so well?How did he know what we wanted to do at the first place? #line:09d0d1a 
Zig:Things are getting more interesting,we just keep playing with him,I want to see how this ends... #line:0af2f07 
Zig:hehehehe... #line:002b260 
===

title:Main_001_05
---
CinderTail:Well,well,well,looks who's here.
CinderTail:Few tiny little bugs dare to infiltrate the lab.
CinderTail:And what do  Looks like an arm isn't enough to teach you a lesson,eh?
Zig:What the... Sam? You met before?
Rigel:...
CinderTail:Sam? HAHAHAHAAAAAAAAA!!!
CinderTail:A cute nickname you picked for yourself...RIGEL.
Zig&Zag:What???
Zig:So you are telling me we are doing business with the "DEMON" all the time?
Zag:...you...you are alive?
Rigel:Listen,whatever my identity is,we have to save our life first!
CinderTail:Hahahahaha!!You'd better listen to him!

===

title:Intro_CinderTail
---
CinderTail:Finally,you came. #line:0a7bd1e 
Rigel:Captain?Captain!! #line:04cbda1 
Captain:Run...Rigel... #line:08d2dd7 
CinderTail:Looks like your Captain's life maintanence system is failing. #line:0f092f9 
CinderTail:His lung is broken and oxygen is running out.5 minutes.If you can beat me in 5 minutes,maybe your captain will live. #line:06d304b 
CinderTail:Or you can walk away now,I will pretend nothing happened. #line:00b20d3 
Rigel:Captain!!Arhhhhhhhhh!!!! #line:06da880 
Captain:Run... #line:05db81a 
CinderTail:Calm down,little mouse,anger can solve nothing. #line:0512258 
CinderTail:Let's dance. #line:000c3ce 
