title:Past_Memory
---
Rigel:This photo is taken before the war... #line:0673ce4 
Rigel:ORION...A special force that consisted of nine best warriors from the country.I was one of them. #line:0ae832b 
Rigel:...and I am the only one who lived. #line:0b04fb2 
Rigel:Every time I look at the picture,I feel like they are watching me from the hell. #line:0402d4a 
Rigel:This is a curse,and I have to live with that curse for the rest of my life... #line:099332f 
===

title:Lab_First
---
