title:First_Scene_02
---
Meissa:(Scream and Gunfire) #line:027ca48 
Meissa:something is not right here,we have been sent to the trap! #line:0257536 
Meissa:We are being ambushed,Rigel,don't go to that coordination!I repeat... #line:0024c73 
Rigel:Captain,you are okay? #line:047220b 
Rigel:Captain! #line:02e22e1 
Rigel:We have to save him! #line:03315d7 
Soilder A:This is suicide,we have to retreat! #line:08b78f2 
Soilder B:We didn't rest since last night.I can't.., #line:03f1285 
Rigel:This is an order!Captain always treats you well,this is how you repay him? #line:080b210 
Soilder A:But... #line:099bdf4 
Rigel:I said,this is an ORDER.Follow me. #line:0463ef4 
===

title:Plant_Shop_01
---
Simon:Uncle Rigel! #line:0f90a0d 
Rigel:Simon? It's 9 P.M. you should be at school! #line:047f223 
Simon:But I don't want to go there!All we do in the class is hearing teacher repeating the E-books! #line:0542f35 
Simon:Please,uncle rigel!!! Let me stay at your shop! #line:0f76d6b 
Simon:You told me you escape from class at my age,right? #line:00c9056 
Rigel:Yes,my elder brother was very mad at me... #line:0f3faa7 
Simon:See?You don't have the right to tell me to go to the school. #line:055decf 
Rigel:But escape from school is not right,only this time,and don't tell anyone,okay? #line:00667d0 
Simon:Uncle Rigel!You are the best! #line:0d41cae 
Rigel:There's a huge update in "Star Farer", Let's play. #line:0bad8db 
===

title:Plant_Shop_02
---
Simon:Uncle Rigel,you have an elder brother? #line:0db33cf 
Rigel:Yes...but we don't have any blood ties,he's a rabbit. #line:0f67f46 
Simon:Cool!So you are in the same school? #line:068b08e 
Rigel:Yes...in some ways. #line:0e679ce 
Rigel:He was good at almost everything,but your uncle Rigel...He skipped classes. #line:00535fb 
Simon:As am I,now we are on the same boat,uncle Rigel! #line:0a2fafb 
Simon:So is your brother doing fine?Can I meet him? #line:02b53d5 
Rigel:He...diappeared during the war,I tried to find him...but with no avail. #line:0bbc16d 
Simon:Oh...I'm sorry to hear that,uncle Rigel. #line:0760035 
Rigel:It's okay...Hey,there's a boss fight ahead,no sad words! #line:0399d8e 
Simon:Roger that,uncle Rigel! #line:0ac85d1 
===

title:Plant_Shop_03
---
Simon:WOW!Uncle Rigel!You just shoot the boss down from the sky,how did you do that? #line:0f25bea 
Rigel:I have talent in shooting,I was in the shooting club back in the school. #line:06e7fa9 
Simon:That's so cool!I can't beat the boss with my other 3 friends with the legendary equipment, but you can do it singlehandly with a common gun! #line:086b8e2 
Rigel:Well...I have been playing shooting games for a long time... #line:08ada7c 
Simon's Mom:Simon? #line:03de0d6 
Simon:Coming,Mom! #line:0521123 
Simon's Mom:Rigel,thank you again for taking care of Simon while I am working,is he doing fine? #line:06c9148 
Rigel:Y...Yes,he told me he got first place at the swimming lesson today. #line:033b2a3 
Simon:(Wink at Rigel)Yes,it was tense! #line:0ab8b32 
Simon's Mom:That is my good boy! #line:073bd20 
Regel:How is your new job in neon city,Mrs. Simon? #line:001d23a 
Simon's Mom:Well...My boss is a good mammal,he is very kind to me and I am learning a lot from him.Thanks for asking. #line:0c0e51e 
Rigel:That's good to hear.See you tomorrow! #line:051d44a 
Simon:Bye,uncle Rigel!See you tomorrow! #line:063ddd7 
Rigel:It's 6 P.M. already,I will close the shop and grab a drink at the bar,the nightmare was so real... #line:0e82e5e 
===

title:Bar_01
---
Raccoon:A Neon Legend? #line:0a6e5a0 
Rigel:With L size. #line:0b5799f 
Raccoon:Had a nightmare again,hadn't you? #line:0036d94 
Rigel:Yes,But this time was so real,it's just like the dream is extracted from my memory. #line:08f6ac8 
Raccoon:It's about MEISSA,right? #line:057ee57 
Rigel:Yeah...I saw the life ran out his eyes slowly but I couldn't do anything. #line:077cc64 
Rigel:And that wrong coordination,captain is always cautious...how did he walked into that trap? #line:0dd8a74 
Raccoon:But he's not certainly dead,is he?Official announced his death after 3 years of searching but didn't find his BODY. #line:03de45f 
Rigel:I searched everywhere I can but didn't find a single clue. #line:04c9679 
Raccoon:You want to hear my opinion? #line:02ef5ef 
Rigel;What's that? #line:0999be5 
Raccoon:I believe he's still alive,I think there's a reason that he didn't come out. #line:060a83d 
Raccoon:I was served at A01 Battalion during the war,I saw how he fight in the battlefield. #line:028ece5 
Raccoon:He's always calm and cunning,and planted with cutting-edge implants,he can't die that easily. #line:0901adc 
Raccoon:If the bugs got him,they would propogate this in their media,but they didn't,which is werid. #line:060251c 
Rigel:Yeah,you are right... #line:0835117 
Raccoon:Holding up,Rigel.Meissa don't want to see you like this. #line:00ab1db 
Raccoon:After all,you are the last member of the ORION.The hero of mammal country. #line:0602066 
Rigel:... #line:099b923 
Rigel:It's late now,better go home... #line:006ae23 
===

title:Side_02_002_02
---
Rigel:The body has been dealt with,but I can still take a look.
Rigel:There's some body tissue sticked on the ground.
Rigel:The victim was beat down by the suspect,and stomped to death.There are something alongside the tissue...
Rigel:Nano fiber...So the victim was an elite soilder.Only they can wear these things.
Rigel:This is getting more interesting.
===

title:Side_02_002_03
---
Rigel:There's blood spilled on the ground,I come to the right direction.
Rigel:Let me take a sample...
Rigel:Looks like there's stimulant in the blood.
Rigel:Strange,when someone is on the verge of collapsing,they should inject tranquilizer...
Rigel:He's making himself higher,Why?
===

title:Side_02_002_04
---
Police:Don't come any closer,mammal!
Police:Wait...you are the one Officer Sif told us on the comms.
Police:We follow the trace,and found the psycho dumping something in the trash bin...
Police:And he found us,ran into the building straightly. 
Police:There's no exit except the door in the strcture,so there is no escape for him.
Rigel:How was his mental state when you spot him?
Police:He seems rather...calm.We are in the department of Cyberpsychosis so we are familiar with it.That's strange.
Rigel:Yes,Let me talk with him.
Police:Are you out of your mind? You can get yourself killed!
Rigel:This is more complicated than we think,If I run into any trouble,I will call you.
Police:Fine...but that's all we can do.
<<progress_objective "Side_02_002*01">>
===

title:Side_02_002_05
---
Rigel:There're something in the trash bin.
Rigel:Lab Equipment,the description on it says it's from...
Rigel:Central Lab of Rust City!
Rigel:!!!
Rigel:We are getting somewhere.
===

title:Side_02_002_06
---
???:A mammal? So they are sending a mammal to kill me...
Rigel:I'm not one of them.And I'm not with the police too,I mean no harm.
???:So who are you?
Rigel:You are not a Cyberpsychosis.someone MADE you that.Am I right?
???:...
???:Come here,we will talk.
<<progress_objective "Side_02_002*02">>
===


title:Side_02_002_07
---
???:You are my life-saver!Name's cole,an formal engineer.
Rigel:Sam.Tell me everything.
Cole:You were right at the entrance.
Cole:A few days ago,A commission posted on the net that an experiment is recuirting for volunteer...with a decent price.
Rigel:So you signed up.
Cole:Correct.
Cole:At the day of the experiment,some armed soilders knocked my door,blindfolded my eyes and took me onto a car.
Cole:And they took us to a lab,where each of us was locked into an isolation room.
Cole:Then they started to inject something to us.
Cole:After about 2 minutes,I heard someone is screaming in agony next to my room,and then gunfire.
Cole:Shortly after that,I blacked out.
Rigel:After you come back to sense,you found yourself covered in blood,with lab equipment attached to your body.
Rigel:And a couple of armed forces tried to kill you, but you fought back, which is the body that sticked to the ground in front of the restaurant in rust city.
Cole:Exactly,how did you know that? Who are you exactly?
Rigel:A private detective who loves to meddle in others' affairs,nothing more.
<<jump Side_02_002_08>>
===

title:Side_02_002_08
---
Rigel:Let me sort things out for a little bit.
Rigel:So Lion lieutenant was right,the central lab is developing a method to trigger Cyberpsychosis, which can largely improve target's physical capability.
Rigel:The power is strong enough to let Cole,a weak engineer to kill an elite soilder with ease.
Rigel:But for the side effect,cole also lost his senses,making him an uncontrollable beast.
Rigel:Which means the experiment didn't go well,so they are going to do anything to cover this up.
Rigel:This is not good for cole,but a good chance for me to gain access to the lab.
<<jump Side_02_002_09>>
===

title:Side_02_002_09
---
Rigel:You get yourself into a quiet big trouble,man.
Rigel:This is the central lab's experiment,and the lab works mainly on important projects for the government and the country.
Rigel:They would do everything to hold back the Cyberpsychosis experiment,which means you are their primary target.
Cole:Please!You have to help me!!
Sif:Little mouse,Have you found the psycho?
Sif:Me and my team is gathering outside the building,we are ready to strike at any time.
Rigel:No need,I found he has already burnt himself into a pile of ash.
Rigel:With a cyber arm...
Sif:Oh...Nice job,after getting out,me and my team will deal with the rest.
Sif:We owe you.
Rigel:Hand me your left limb,and your data chip,if you want to live.
Rigel:Shut down all your devices and cyber addons.Find something that can hide your face and sneak out at night.
Rigel:Go to the location in the sewer,There's a man who called himself Zig,find him,tell him Sam sent you,and you know something about the lab. 
